lu.softec.maven.mavenizer.mavenfile
Class MavenFile

java.lang.Object
  lu.softec.maven.mavenizer.mavenfile.MavenFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
public class MavenFile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable

A Object that hold a library file with its maven coordinates and dependencies. This object is not mutable. Constructing useful instances of this object needs an appropriate factory implementing MavenFileFactory or needs a derived mutable class.
